bankcli/
│
├── bankapp/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── main.py         # Typer CLI logic
│   ├── db.py           # Persistence and authentication logic
│   ├── models.py       # Your updated Account model
│   ├── security.py     # PIN hashing/verification
│
├── accounts.json       # JSON-based persistent storage
├── bankcli.py          # CLI entrypoint (for testing)
├── requirements.txt
├── README.md
├── pyproject.toml      # For building/installing CLI
└── setup.py            # CLI installation config




Installation of the bank app:

pip install -e .          # Execute this where ever .toml file is found